  <p>...we need to learn and practice three new words: "Good" "Wrong" and "Free." Knowing when to say them to your dog is important. If all these flowcharts is raising your blood pressure a bit, skip down to <a href="#bigger-picture">THE BIGGER PICTURE</a> section at the bottom of this page. That's the vision for what we're after here. This may feel clunky at first but it'll feel natural later.</p>
